    <h1>Privacy Policy for Voyant Stays</h1>
    <p><em>Last Updated: August 7, 2025</em></p>

    <p>Welcome to Voyant Stays ("we," "us," or "our"). We are committed to protecting your personal information and your right to privacy. If you have any questions or concerns about this privacy notice, or our practices with regards to your personal information, please contact us at manasrose1058@gmail.com.</p>
    <p>This privacy notice describes how we might use your information if you visit our website at localhost:5000 (and any other domains we own) or otherwise use our services. It is designed to help you understand what information we collect, how we use it, and what rights you have in relation to it.</p>

    <h2 class="mt-4">1. What Information Do We Collect?</h2>
    <p>We collect personal information that you voluntarily provide to us when you register on the website, create a listing, make a booking, or communicate with other users.</p>
    
    <h4>Information You Provide to Us:</h4>
    <ul>
        <li><strong>Account Information:</strong> When you sign up for a Voyant Stays account, we require certain information such as your first name, last name, username, and email address.</li>
        <li><strong>Listing Information:</strong> If you are a Host, we collect detailed information about your property, including its physical address, description, photos, and pricing.</li>
        <li><strong>Booking Information:</strong> When you book a property as a Guest, we collect information related to the transaction, such as booking dates and the number of guests.</li>
        <li><strong>Payment Information:</strong> While we do not store full credit card numbers, we may collect information necessary to process payments, which is handled by our third-party payment processors.</li>
        <li><strong>Communications:</strong> We collect information from your communications with other users through our platform (e.g., messages between a Host and Guest).</li>
        <li><strong>Reviews and Ratings:</strong> We collect reviews, ratings, and comments that you provide about listings or your experiences.</li>
    </ul>

    <h4>Information We Automatically Collect:</h4>
    <ul>
        <li><strong>Log Data and Device Information:</strong> We automatically collect log data when you access and use our website. This information includes your IP address, browser type, operating system, and pages visited.</li>
        <li><strong>Cookies and Similar Technologies:</strong> We use cookies to store information about your preferences and to personalize your experience on our site.</li>
        <li><strong>Geolocation Information:</strong> We use services like Mapbox to process location information for displaying listings on a map. We may collect information about your approximate location from your IP address.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="mt-4">2. How Do We Use Your Information?</h2>
    <p>We use the information we collect for a variety of business purposes, including:</p>
    <ul>
        <li><strong>To Provide and Improve Our Services:</strong> To operate and maintain the Voyant Stays platform, including enabling you to search for, book, and host properties.</li>
        <li><strong>To Enable Bookings:</strong> To facilitate communication between Hosts and Guests and to manage reservations.</li>
        <li><strong>For Security and Fraud Prevention:</strong> To detect and prevent fraud, spam, abuse, security incidents, and other harmful activity.</li>
        <li><strong>To Personalize Your Experience:</strong> To show you content and listings that are relevant to you, such as properties based on your search history.</li>
        <li><strong>For Customer Support:</strong> To resolve technical issues and answer your inquiries.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="mt-4">3. How Is Your Information Shared?</h2>
    <p>We do not sell your personal information. We may share it in the following situations:</p>
    <ul>
        <li><strong>With Other Users:</strong> When you make a booking, we share relevant information (like your name) with the Host to facilitate the reservation. When you create a listing, information you provide is made public to other users.</li>
        <li><strong>With Third-Party Service Providers:</strong> We use third-party services for functions like payment processing (e.g., Stripe) and map services (e.g., Mapbox). These providers only have access to the information necessary to perform their functions.</li>
        <li><strong>For Legal Compliance:</strong> We may disclose your information if we are legally required to do so to comply with applicable law, a judicial proceeding, court order, or other legal process.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="mt-4">4. Your Rights and Choices</h2>
    <p>You have certain rights regarding your personal information. You may review, change, or terminate your account at any time. You can also control the use of cookies at the browser level.</p>

    <h2 class="mt-4">5. Data Security</h2>
    <p>We use administrative, technical, and physical security measures to help protect your personal information. While we have taken reasonable steps to secure the personal information you provide to us, please be aware that no security measures are perfect or impenetrable.</p>

    <h2 class="mt-4">6. Changes to This Privacy Policy</h2>
    <p>We may update this privacy notice from time to time. The updated version will be indicated by a revised "Last Updated" date. We encourage you to review this privacy policy frequently to be informed of how we are protecting your information.</p>

    <h2 class="mt-4">7. Contact Us</h2>
    <p>If you have questions or comments about this notice, you may email us at <strong>manasrose1058@gmail.com</strong>.</p>

